== Biography
I am a Ph. D. student in [https://www.medphysics.wisc.edu/wp/research/ct/ CT research group] in Department of Medical Physics at University of Wisconsin-Madison advised by [https://www.medphysics.wisc.edu/wp/blog/staff/chen-guanghong/ Dr. Guang-Hong Chen]. My research projects are related to x-ray imaging systems and algorithms. My Google Scholar page can be found [https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=b-S9VEMAAAAJ&hl=en /here/]. 

